1. *Spoj* je osiguran kroz zaštitnu cev. (The *connection* is secured through a protective tube.)
2. Razmotrite *spoj* između ove dve ideje. (Consider the *link* between these two ideas.)
3. Radnik je uspeo da napravi dobar *spoj* između dva dela mašine. (The worker managed to make a good *joint* between two machine parts.)
4. *Spoj* kablova je urađen na najbolji mogući način. (The *joining* of cables was done in the best possible way.)
5. Ovaj materijal ne može da se *spoji* sa drugim metalima. (This material cannot be *connected* with other metals.)
6. Planiram da *spojim* ova dva događaja u jednu priču. (I plan to *combine* these two events into one story.)
7. Sutradan će se *spojiti* više grupa u jednu. (Tomorrow, several groups will *merge* into one.)
8. Molim vas da *spoje* te dve utičnice. (Please *connect* those two sockets.)
9. Naučnik je pokušao da *spoji* dve različite teorije. (The scientist tried to *unite* two different theories.)
10. Da li možete da mi pomognete da *spoje* ova dva dela slagalice? (Can you help me *join* these two puzzle pieces?)